### Usage
Basic example:

```html
<div class="timer" data-seconds-left=800></div>

<script src="jquery.js"></script>
<script src="simple.timer.js"></script>
<script>
  $(function(){
    $('.timer').startTimer();
  });
</script>
```

Use the `onComplete` option for custom behavior:

```javascript
$('.timer').startTimer({
  onComplete: function(){
    console.log('Done!');
  }
});
```

### Tests
QUnit tests can be run by opening the `tests/index.html` file from a browser.
